{"tid":1913441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微信將「習近平」列關鍵字黑名單！學者曝：避免領導人尷尬","createTime":"2020-03-06T19:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T08:41:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"902691ccef676d86f9d7e863c6cd203488e792d5","tid":1913441,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T19:31:31.000Z","msg":"微信將「習近平」列關鍵字黑名單！學者曝：避免領導人尷尬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=702618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D702618&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=2b8dcb67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D702618&h=76febe4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=702618</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）全球爆發後，各界紛紛苛責中國並未及時揭露疫情，雖然北京當局矢口否認，但網路上質疑聲音不斷，沒多久這些訊息又消失。對此，加拿大多倫多大學公民實驗室（Citizen Lab）發表的最新研究指出，中國社群平台的言論審查，有高比例涉及「習近平」的關鍵字遭到屏蔽，其中也包含李文亮、P4病毒實驗室、港澳台防疫工作等關鍵字遭禁。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，多倫多大學公民實驗室3日發表研究《審查傳染病：中國社交媒體如何管理關於新冠病毒的訊息》，此研究針對中國直播平台「YY」以及社交平台「微博」上的關鍵字進行分析。發現YY將45個關鍵字列入黑名單，包含「武漢不明肺炎」、「武漢海鮮市場」、「沙士變異」、「爆發SARS疫情」、「武漢衛生委員會」、「P4病毒實驗室」等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而微信更加嚴厲，研究發現，從1月１日開始連續六週，共禁止516組關鍵詞，包含「中國政府防疫措施」、「港澳台防疫工作」、「李文亮事件」等。其中192組關鍵字涉及政府官員，有87%與 「習近平」有關，包含「習近平到武漢」、「習近平＋形式主義＋防疫」、「某人＋親自」、「習近平＋疫情蔓延」等組合。<br />\n<br />\n研究也指出，吹哨者李文亮醫生過世引起軒然大波，中國網友紛紛表達哀悼與憤慨，並且爭取言論自由的聲音不斷；對此，微信禁止19組關鍵字，包含「疫情+顏色革命+李文亮」、「聲音+人傳人+李文亮」、「武漢+五大訴求」等。<br />\n<br />\n結論推測，自從疫情爆發後，中國領導人強調「輿論導向以及掌握新聞的領導權」，這一方面是為了降低人民的恐慌；另一方面是避免領導人尷尬，以維持中共政府的威信。"},{"pid":"a479ced0d785b078759d0807dc55ef0a2a566882","tid":1913441,"uid":96708,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T21:18:45.000Z","msg":"羽斤干"},{"pid":"5ef12b88c9699d30f1cae76581dc8239c671043d","tid":1913441,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T22:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b6f39736a64a01f587dd118ed8a591fb257089","tid":1913441,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a479ced0d785b078759d0807dc55ef0a2a566882","tid":1913441,"uid":96708,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T21:18:45.000Z","msg":"羽斤干"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T22:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8e4fef208c5fd6c96b2909be7986986c233c90","tid":1913441,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a479ced0d785b078759d0807dc55ef0a2a566882","tid":1913441,"uid":96708,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T21:18:45.000Z","msg":"羽斤干"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T22:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841ba17dd6b8c8a59f08c44113efda9feb5d3314","tid":1913441,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a479ced0d785b078759d0807dc55ef0a2a566882","tid":1913441,"uid":96708,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T21:18:45.000Z","msg":"羽斤干"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T22:54:32.000Z","msg":"、、、"},{"pid":"6059a9dff8f04a51a3652d9993b54ac64c09d8d4","tid":1913441,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T22:55:15.000Z","msg":"吸精瓶"},{"pid":"ec16dc0b9a08614e92815f749146265a61856446","tid":1913441,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T22:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSHUFhwsmRXAyTB38XA4BZDQcv1K6iJs_FzZf-ZZlLOXS_nAFbI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcSHUFhwsmRXAyTB38XA4BZDQcv1K6iJs_FzZf-ZZlLOXS_nAFbI&h=934747c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nXxx"},{"pid":"9d8f00b00cdec4ae45dad023f902c47cc0cb